@startuml referral_attribution_flow
'==============================================================
' Referral Attribution Complete Logic
' Referral 归因逻辑全流程
'==============================================================

title **Referral 归因逻辑全流程**\nReferral Attribution Complete Flow

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #78716C
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #FFF
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #78716C
skinparam PartitionBackgroundColor #FAFAF9
skinparam PartitionBorderColor #A8A29E
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam NoteBorderColor #F59E0B
skinparam ArrowColor #57534E

|#F0FDFA|User 用户|
|#EFF6FF|Frontend 前端|
|#FDF4FF|Games Backend 游戏后端|
|#FFF7ED|External Systems 外部系统|

|User 用户|
start
:用户点击 Referral 分享链接
User clicks Referral sharing link;

:用户执行一系列动作（当日内）
User performs actions (**same day**):
• 下载 App / Download App
• 打开 App / Open App
• 注册账号 / Register account;

|Frontend 前端|
:用户进入游戏落地页，触发归因校验
User enters game landing page,
triggering attribution check;

|Games Backend 游戏后端|
partition "**三路 OR 归因校验 / 3-Path OR Attribution Check**" {

    partition "路径 ① 下载归因 / Path 1: Download Attribution (MMP)" #EFF6FF {
        |External Systems 外部系统|
        :查询 MMP 归因数据（通过 userid）
        Query MMP attribution data via userid;
        note right
            **实现细节 / Implementation**
            ① 分享链接携带 MMP 追踪参数
            ② 用户通过链接下载 App，MMP 上报
            ③ 用户注册后，MMP 关联 userid
            ④ Games 通过 userid 查询 MMP Kafka
        end note

        |Games Backend 游戏后端|
        if (MMP 归因记录存在？\nMMP record exists?) then (Yes)
            :download_result = **PASS** ✅;
        else (No)
            :download_result = **FAIL** ❌;
        endif
    }

    partition "路径 ② 激活归因 / Path 2: Activation Attribution (utm)" #F5F3FF {
        |External Systems 外部系统|
        :监听 signup 消息，获取 deviceid
        Monitor signup, get deviceid via userid;

        :查询该 deviceid 当日最早 utm 来源
        Query earliest utm source today
        for this deviceid (Traffic Kafka);
        note right
            **实现细节 / Implementation**
            ① 分享链接携带 utm 参数
            ② 链接打开时进行 utm 上报
            ③ Games 监听 signup 消息
            ④ 通过 userid → deviceid 关联
            ⑤ 查询 deviceid 当日最早 utm
        end note

        |Games Backend 游戏后端|
        if (最早 utm 来源 = Referral？\nEarliest utm = Referral?) then (Yes)
            :activate_result = **PASS** ✅;
        else (No)
            :activate_result = **FAIL** ❌;
        endif
    }

    partition "路径 ③ 注册归因 / Path 3: Registration Attribution (Deeplink)" #F0FDFA {
        |Games Backend 游戏后端|
        :记录用户通过 Deeplink 进入游戏页面的时间
        Record game page entry time via Deeplink;

        :查询用户当日最早登录/注册时间
        Query user's earliest login/registration
        time today;
        note right
            **实现细节 / Implementation**
            ① 用户通过 Deeplink 唤起 App
            ② 游戏弹出登录/注册面板
            ③ 用户完成注册后返回游戏
            ④ 比较注册时间 vs 页面进入时间
        end note

        if (注册时间 > 页面进入时间？\nRegistration time > entry time?) then (Yes)
            :register_result = **PASS** ✅;
        else (No)
            :register_result = **FAIL** ❌;
        endif
    }

    '--- OR Logic Decision ---
    if (**OR 逻辑：任一路径通过？**\n**Any path PASS? (OR logic)**\ndownload OR activate OR register) then (<color:green><b>Yes - 至少一路通过</b></color>)
    else (<color:red><b>No - 全部自然量 All organic</b></color>)
        #FFEBEE:三路均未溯源到 Referral
        All 3 paths failed to trace to Referral;
        :视为 **Existing User**
        Treated as **Existing User**
        不发放邀请奖励 / No referral reward;
        |User 用户|
        #FFCDD2:用户以 Existing User 身份参与活动
        User participates as Existing User;
        stop
    endif
}

partition "**身份校验 / Identity Verification (UPP)**" {
    |External Systems 外部系统|
    :通过 UPP 查询用户 Tag
    Query user tags via UPP;
    note right
        **New User 判定**
        Tag ID: 23
        Days since Shopee registration = 0
        ----
        **RA User 判定**
        具体唤醒规则标签（待确认）
    end note

    |Games Backend 游戏后端|
    if (Days since registration = 0?\n注册天数 = 0？(Tag ID 23)) then (Yes)
        :user_type = **New User** 新用户;
    elseif (RA 规则匹配？\nRA rules matched?) then (Yes)
        :user_type = **Reactivated User** 唤醒用户;
    else (<color:red>Neither 均不满足</color>)
        #FFEBEE:UPP 校验未通过：非当日新用户/RA 用户
        UPP check failed: not same-day New/RA;
        :视为 **Existing User**
        Treated as **Existing User**;
        |User 用户|
        #FFCDD2:用户以 Existing User 身份参与活动
        User participates as Existing User;
        stop
    endif
}

|Games Backend 游戏后端|
#C8E6C9:**归因成功 / Attribution Success** ✅
用户身份：New User 或 RA User
归因路径：至少一条 Referral 路径验证通过;

partition "**奖励持久化与发放 / Reward Persistence & Issuance**" #FFF8E1 {

    :将归因结果写入数据库
    Write attribution record to DB;
    note right
        **归因记录 / Attribution Record**
        ════════════════════════════
        | **Field**            | **Value**            |
        | User UID          | 被邀请用户标识      |
        | Attribution Type  | New / Reactivated    |
        | Referrer UID      | 邀请人标识           |
        | Attribution Status| **Pending**          |
    end note

    |User 用户|
    :用户进入游戏（当天或之后任意时间）
    User enters game
    (same day **or any future day**);

    |Games Backend 游戏后端|
    :查询该用户是否有 Pending 归因记录
    Query for Pending attribution records;

    if (存在 Pending 记录？\nPending record exists?) then (Yes)
        :按归因身份类型发放对应奖励
        Issue reward based on attribution type
        (New User reward / RA User reward);

        :更新状态 Pending → **Rewarded**
        Update status to **Rewarded**;

        |User 用户|
        #C8E6C9:🎉 用户领取 Referral 奖励
        User receives Referral reward;
        note right
            **关键规则 / Key Rules**
            ① 奖励与归因日期解耦
               Reward decoupled from attribution day
            ② 仅首次进入游戏时触发
               Only triggered on first game entry
            ③ 一旦领取，归因关系失效
               Once claimed, cannot re-trigger
        end note
    else (No)
        :无待发放记录
        No pending record;
    endif
}

stop

@enduml


@startuml edge_case_crossday
'==============================================================
' Edge Case 1: Cross-day Attribution Failure
' 边界场景 1：跨日归因失效
'==============================================================

title **边界场景 1：跨日归因失效**\nEdge Case 1: Cross-day Attribution Window Expiry

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam SequenceGroupBackgroundColor #FAFAF9
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam NoteBorderColor #F59E0B

actor "User\n用户" as U
participant "Referral Link\n分享链接" as RL
participant "App" as APP
participant "Games Backend\n游戏后端" as GB
participant "UPP" as UPP

== **昨天 / Yesterday** ==

U -> RL : 点击 Referral 链接\nClick referral link
RL -> APP : 跳转至应用商店\nRedirect to app store
U -> APP : 下载并注册\nDownload & register
note over APP : 用户成为 **新用户**\nUser becomes **New User**\n(Days since registration = 0)

== **今天 / Today** ==

U -> APP : 打开 App
APP -> GB : 进入游戏落地页\nEnter game landing page
GB -> UPP : 查询用户 Tag\nQuery user tags

UPP --> GB : Days since registration = **1** ❌\n(不再是 0 / No longer 0)

note over GB #FFEBEE
    **归因失败 / Attribution Failed**
    注册发生在"昨天"，今天进入时
    Tag 已更新为 Days = 1
    不满足当日新用户条件
    ----
    Registration was "yesterday",
    tag now shows Days = 1,
    same-day New User condition NOT met
end note

GB --> U : 视为 Existing User\nTreated as Existing User

@enduml


@startuml edge_case_last_click
'==============================================================
' Edge Case 2: Last Click Wins
' 边界场景 2：最后点击有效（截胡）
'==============================================================

title **边界场景 2："最后点击有效"原则**\nEdge Case 2: Last Click Wins

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam SequenceGroupBackgroundColor #FAFAF9
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam NoteBorderColor #F59E0B

actor "User\n用户" as U
participant "Referrer A\n邀请人 A" as RA
participant "Referrer B\n邀请人 B" as RB
participant "App" as APP
participant "Games Backend\n游戏后端" as GB

== **同一天内 / Same Day** ==

U -> RA : ① 点击 A 的分享链接\nClick A's referral link
RA -> APP : 跳转下载\nRedirect to download
U -> APP : ② 下载 App\nDownload App

... 一段时间后 / Some time later ...

U -> RB : ③ 点击 B 的分享链接\nClick B's referral link
RB -> APP : 唤起 App\nOpen App via deeplink
U -> APP : ④ 进入活动落地页\nEnter campaign landing page
APP -> GB : 触发归因校验\nTrigger attribution check

note over GB #E8F5E9
    **归因结果 / Attribution Result**
    用户认定为新用户 ✅
    User identified as New User ✅
    ----
    奖励归属：**邀请人 B** 🏆
    Reward goes to: **Referrer B**
    ----
    原因：B 的链接触发了最终归因校验
    Reason: B's link triggered the
    final attribution check
end note

GB --> RB : 发放邀请奖励\nIssue referral reward 🏆
GB --> RA : 无奖励\nNo reward ✗

@enduml


@startuml edge_case_indirect
'==============================================================
' Edge Case 3: Indirect Path (3-Path OR)
' 边界场景 3：迂回路径（三路 OR 验证）
'==============================================================

title **边界场景 3：迂回路径（三路 OR 验证）**\nEdge Case 3: Indirect Path with 3-Path OR

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam SequenceGroupBackgroundColor #FAFAF9
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam NoteBorderColor #F59E0B

actor "User\n用户" as U
participant "Referral Link\n分享链接" as RL
participant "App" as APP
participant "Games Backend\n游戏后端" as GB
participant "MMP" as MMP
participant "Traffic Kafka" as TK
participant "UPP" as UPP

== **用户动作 / User Actions (同一天 Same Day)** ==

U -> RL : ① 点击 Referral 链接\nClick Referral link
RL -> APP : 跳转下载\nRedirect to download
U -> APP : 下载 App\nDownload App
MMP -> MMP : MMP 记录下载来源\nMMP records download source

U -> APP : ② 直接点桌面图标打开 App\nDirectly tap icon to open App
U -> APP : 注册账号\nRegister account
note over APP : 激活非链接触发\nActivation NOT via link

U -> RL : ③ 再次点击 Referral 链接\nClick Referral link again
RL -> APP : 唤起进入游戏\nDeeplink into game

== **系统校验 / System Verification** ==

GB -> UPP : 1. UPP 身份校验\nIdentity check
UPP --> GB : Days = 0 → **New User** ✅

GB -> MMP : 2. 路径① 下载校验\nPath 1: Download check
MMP --> GB : MMP 记录存在 → **PASS** ✅

GB -> TK : 3. 路径② 激活校验\nPath 2: Activation check
TK --> GB : 首次打开非链接 → **FAIL** ❌

GB -> GB : 4. 路径③ 注册校验\nPath 3: Registration check
note over GB : 注册发生在 Deeplink 进入之前\nRegistration before Deeplink entry → **FAIL** ❌

note over GB #E8F5E9
    **应用 OR 逻辑 / Apply OR Logic**
    ════════════════════════════
    路径① 下载：✅ PASS
    路径② 激活：❌ FAIL
    路径③ 注册：❌ FAIL
    ----
    **至少一路通过 → 归因成功** ✅
    At least one path passed → Success
    ----
    New User + Download via Referral
    其余路径不影响结果
end note

GB -> GB : 写入归因记录 (Pending)\nWrite attribution record

@enduml


@startuml reward_state_machine
'==============================================================
' Reward Status Lifecycle
' 奖励状态生命周期
'==============================================================

title **归因记录状态流转**\nAttribution Record Status Lifecycle

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam StateBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
skinparam StateBorderColor #78716C
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam NoteBorderColor #F59E0B

[*] --> AttributionCheck : 用户进入落地页\nUser enters landing page

state "归因校验中\nAttribution Check" as AttributionCheck {
    state "三路 OR 校验\n3-Path OR Check" as PathCheck
    state "UPP 身份校验\nUPP Identity Check" as UPPCheck
    PathCheck --> UPPCheck : 至少一路通过\nAt least one path passed
    PathCheck --> [*] : 全部未通过 → Existing User\nAll failed → Existing User
    UPPCheck --> [*] : 非 New/RA → Existing User\nNot New/RA → Existing User
}

AttributionCheck --> Pending : 归因成功\nAttribution Success

state "Pending\n待发放" as Pending #FFF9C4 {
    Pending : User UID = xxx
    Pending : Type = New / RA
    Pending : Referrer UID = yyy
    Pending : Status = **Pending**
}
note right of Pending
    用户可在任意时间
    首次进入游戏触发
    ----
    User can trigger on
    first game entry
    at **any future time**
end note

Pending --> Rewarded : 用户进入游戏，发放奖励\nUser enters game, reward issued

state "Rewarded\n已发放" as Rewarded #C8E6C9 {
    Rewarded : Status = **Rewarded**
    Rewarded : 归因关系终结
    Rewarded : Record finalized
}
note right of Rewarded
    一旦发放，不可再次触发
    Once issued, cannot re-trigger
end note

Rewarded --> [*]

@enduml
